    "4 score-based learning, and Sect. 5 hybrid learning and some non-combinatorial approaches.",
    "Figure 6 provides an overview of the evolution of structure learning algorithms that are covered in this paper, and will be referenced in subsequent sections.",
    "Section 6 covers various practical considerations when applying these algorithms to synthetic and real data, including how to evaluate their output, as well as a discussion of comparative reviews of algorithm performance.",
